1
00:00:15,856 --> 00:00:18,860
片名：鋼鐵擂臺/鐵甲鋼拳

2
00:00:20,860 --> 00:00:21,860
翻譯：閑閑的猛男 校對：目前沒有

3
00:00:27,860 --> 00:00:29,860
翻譯的很辛苦 句句推敲 認為好的按聲贊 但是轉載 請考慮原創的辛苦 不要把原訊息刪掉！

4
00:03:11,708 --> 00:03:15,610
等一下 等一下 來了
Hang on, hang on. Come on.

5
00:03:17,013 --> 00:03:19,948
Charlie你在哪里？更重要的是 幾時還錢？
Where are you, Charlie? More importantly, where is my money?

6
00:03:20,049 --> 00:03:23,382
- 你還欠我三萬元 - Jack 我馬上可以還你
- You're into me for 30 grand. - Jack, I'm going to pay you.

7
00:03:23,486 --> 00:03:25,852
我不是Jack 我是比爾
This ain't Jack! It's Bill Panner.

8
00:03:25,955 --> 00:03:29,482
你還欠Jack錢？你最好先還我
You owe Jack money, too? You pay me first!

9
00:03:29,592 --> 00:03:34,359
比爾 兄弟 錢我準備好了 就在我手上
Bill. We're good, buddy. I got your money. It's right here in my hand.

10
00:03:34,464 --> 00:03:36,364
那我們約個地………
Why don't we meet up on the?

11
00:03:40,937 --> 00:03:43,906
- 喂？你的訊號很差 - 我聽不到你
- Your phone's going all screwy. Hello? - I'm losing you.

12
00:03:44,007 --> 00:03:46,498
我聽不清楚你說什么...
I can't hear what you're say...

13
00:03:48,945 --> 00:03:51,743
先生您好 那個是突擊者號嗎？
Hey, mister. Is that Ambush?

14
00:03:53,449 --> 00:03:55,644
- 是的 - 我們可以看看嗎？
- Yeah. - Can we see him?

15
00:03:56,986 --> 00:03:59,386
- 你們想看？- 耶
- You want to see him? - Yeah.

16
00:03:59,489 --> 00:04:01,753
等一下！
Give me a minute.

17
00:04:07,930 --> 00:04:09,056
這個是...
This...

18
00:04:10,867 --> 00:04:13,529
...突擊者號！ 啟動 啟動！
is Ambush. Wakey, wakey.

19
00:04:33,523 --> 00:04:36,822
- 他要跟誰比賽？- 其實他是要跟...
- What robot is he fighting? - Actually he's going to fight...

20
00:04:36,926 --> 00:04:38,484
噢 小妹妹 你要干嘛？
Whoa, little lady. What are you doing?

21
00:04:38,594 --> 00:04:39,891
我可不可以跟他照個像？
Can we get a picture with him?

22
00:04:39,996 --> 00:04:41,657
當然可以 五塊錢
Sure. For five dollars.

23
00:04:41,764 --> 00:04:43,857
照個像要五元？你開玩笑吧？
You want five dollars? Seriously?

24
00:04:43,966 --> 00:04:46,594
沒開玩笑 馬上給我五元
No, I want five dollars immediately.

25
00:04:46,703 --> 00:04:48,398
走吧！小朋友！
Come on, guys.

26
00:04:49,839 --> 00:04:53,172
- 好啦！我開玩笑的 三元就好 - 你慢慢想吧
- All right, I'm kidding. Three bucks. - Whatever.

27
00:04:53,476 --> 00:04:56,104
- 那就二塊半好了？- 你這個遜?！
- How about $2.50? - You suck!

28
00:04:59,415 --> 00:05:01,747
又是一個鄉巴佬小鎮 是吧？
It's going to be one of those towns, huh?

29
00:05:02,719 --> 00:05:07,588
各位先生女士們 歡迎來到2020年圣蘭卓鄉村市集
Welcome, ladies and gentlemen, to the 2020 San Leandro County Fair.

30
00:05:07,690 --> 00:05:11,148
各位請坐 我們將要開始了
Please take your seats. We're almost ready to get this thing started.

31
00:05:13,463 --> 00:05:15,897
講好的是我的機器人對抗800磅的牛
I was told my bot was fighting an 800-pound steer.

32
00:05:15,998 --> 00:05:18,728
那只牛絕對不止800磅 你這個呆頭
That is not 800 pounds, knucklehead.

33
00:05:18,835 --> 00:05:23,795
Charlie"無所不能小子" 肯頓 看來你也老了 老朋友
Charlie "the Can Do Kid" Kenton. Time has not been good to you, my friend.

34
00:05:23,906 --> 00:05:28,536
- 里奇 麻煩大了 - 不要激動 老朋友
- Ricky, we got a big problem here. - Slow down there, hoss.

35
00:05:28,644 --> 00:05:33,138
最后一次我們的見面是在桑休士頓中心
Last time I saw you, you were staring at the ceiling at the Sam Houston Center

36
00:05:33,449 --> 00:05:35,747
我正好賞你一記右叉拳
with the taste of my right cross all over your face.

37
00:05:37,854 --> 00:05:39,685
- 準備好了嗎？- 耶
- Are we good to go here? - Yeah.

38
00:05:39,789 --> 00:05:43,657
說好的是我的機器人對抗800磅的牛 代價是三千元
We agreed that my boxer would fight an 800-pound steer for three grand.

39
00:05:43,760 --> 00:05:45,489
- 真的嘛？- 是的 說好的是這樣
- Am I right? - Yes, sir. We did.

40
00:05:45,595 --> 00:05:47,620
但是那只牛看起來大概是2000磅
That bull is like 2,000 pounds.

41
00:05:47,730 --> 00:05:49,220
打個商量
I'll tell you something.

42
00:05:49,532 --> 00:05:53,730
如果你的機器人不打 你一分錢都拿不到 怎么樣？
Your bot don't fight, you don't get paid! How about that?

43
00:05:55,605 --> 00:05:57,163
滾吧你！
Get the hell out of here.

44
00:06:01,577 --> 00:06:04,842
要不要賭大一點 我的機器人跟你的牛對打
Why don't we make this more interesting. My bot against your bull, straight up.

45
00:06:04,947 --> 00:06:07,006
- 賭多少？- 二萬 勝方獨贏
- How much? - Twenty grand, winner takes all.

46
00:06:07,116 --> 00:06:09,778
- 二萬？你有錢可以賭？- 藏在我車上
- Twenty grand. You got 20 grand? - In a safe in my truck.

47
00:06:13,222 --> 00:06:14,746
Charlie 好吧！
All right, Charlie.

48
00:06:14,857 --> 00:06:18,987
二萬就二萬 但是如果你輸了繞跑
Twenty grand it is, but if you lose and you welch,

49
00:06:19,095 --> 00:06:21,586
我見你一次就海扁你一次
I'll come after you and beat you to within an inch of your life.

50
00:06:21,697 --> 00:06:23,858
你知道我沒騙你 因為我時常在扁你
You know that I can do that because I already done done it!

51
00:06:23,966 --> 00:06:27,800
別靠我那么那么近 你這個拳擊場上的娘娘腔 到底比不比？
In life you get too close, in the ring you stand back like a girl. Just shake.

52
00:06:28,104 --> 00:06:33,007
那好 握手然后“?” 像以前一樣 你要不要再被我扁？
All right. Shake and pow! Just like that once again. You want to dance again?

53
00:06:33,109 --> 00:06:36,567
幫這家伙加加油 給他點好運 他需要點運氣 耶！
Cheer for this guy. Give him some luck. He needs some luck, y'all.

54
00:06:37,079 --> 00:06:39,673
不要再惹那只牛！
Don't touch that bull.

55
00:06:39,782 --> 00:06:42,876
各位先生女士們 我來問一下；
Ladies and gentlemen, I got to ask,

56
00:06:42,985 --> 00:06:45,545
這里有沒有人是機器人拳擊賽的粉絲？
do we have any fans of robot boxing here today?

57
00:06:48,157 --> 00:06:50,216
各位好朋友 注意聽著 我了解………
Now, listen, friends, I understand

58
00:06:50,526 --> 00:06:54,121
不是每個人都可以付得起300元的門票
we can't all afford to go all the way over there to Dallas

59
00:06:54,230 --> 00:06:59,167
然后一路到達拉斯去看世界杯機器人拳擊大賽！
and pay $300 for one of those World Robot Boxing League fights.

60
00:06:59,268 --> 00:07:02,567
所以我決定給你們帶來一場機器人拳擊比賽
So, I decided that I would bring a robot boxing match

61
00:07:02,672 --> 00:07:06,039
就在這里 我們的圣卓蘭鄉村市集上
right here to our little fair here in San Leandro.

62
00:07:06,142 --> 00:07:07,575
喜歡嗎？
How about that?

63
00:07:10,813 --> 00:07:14,772
各位先生女士們 我來介紹
Ladies and gentlemen, I introduce to you,

64
00:07:14,884 --> 00:07:17,546
突擊者號！
Ambush!

65
00:07:17,653 --> 00:07:18,950
來吧 開始吧！
Let's do it!

66
00:07:21,657 --> 00:07:22,954
好樣的 大家伙
All right, big fella.

67
00:07:28,598 --> 00:07:30,259
他是不是一個大家伙啊？
He's a big fella, ain't he?

68
00:07:30,566 --> 00:07:34,002
轉一圈 讓大家看看你有多威猛！
Take a turn. Let them see how beautiful you are.

69
00:07:38,808 --> 00:07:39,866
看看你有多有力！
Show them some power.

70
00:07:41,010 --> 00:07:43,843
大家趕快看 他在為我們表演功夫喔
Look at that. He's getting all kung fu-y on us.

71
00:07:45,014 --> 00:07:46,276
耶 大家伙！
Yeah, big fella.

72
00:07:46,582 --> 00:07:49,642
突擊者號的對手是年度公牛大賽……
Ambush's opponent today, he's last year's runner-up

73
00:07:49,752 --> 00:07:51,811
擊倒率最高的………
in the baddest of the bulls competition,

74
00:07:51,921 --> 00:07:54,754
各位先生女士們
ladies and gentlemen,

75
00:07:54,857 --> 00:07:57,621
黑色閃電！
Black Thunder!

76
00:07:59,028 --> 00:08:01,758
- 開始吧 - 戰斗開始咯
- Let's get it on! - Let's get this thing started.

77
00:08:05,234 --> 00:08:06,963
你就這么點能耐？
Is that all you got?

78
00:08:08,104 --> 00:08:10,937
耶！兄弟 干勁拿出來！
Yeah, brother. Bring it on.

79
00:08:20,883 --> 00:08:22,282
干掉他 干掉他！
Take him, take him.

80
00:08:23,819 --> 00:08:27,220
突擊者一掌把這只憤怒的牛翻倒在地
Ambush lays the smackdown on that prime beef.

81
00:08:33,062 --> 00:08:35,155
我還有很多絕招 大家伙 我們才剛暖身
I got more for you, big fella. We're just getting started.

82
00:08:38,634 --> 00:08:40,124
準備 現在 跳
OK. Jump, now!

83
00:08:48,177 --> 00:08:49,804
突擊者一摑掀翻黑色閃電
Ambush, decks Black Thunder,

84
00:08:49,912 --> 00:08:53,211
但是當你惹毛一只公牛 你就最好小心他們的牛角
but when you mess with the bull, you're going to get the horns.

85
00:08:56,052 --> 00:08:58,350
噢 你喜歡是吧！我看得出來 妳喜歡這個
You like that. I can tell. You like that.

86
00:09:00,256 --> 00:09:01,382
轉身小心
Turn around!

87
00:09:05,194 --> 00:09:07,822
里奇！里奇！夠了我們認輸！
Ricky! Ricky, stop this thing!

88
00:09:18,007 --> 00:09:20,874
來吧！我們還要戰斗 跳 跳一下 ！
Come on. We're still in this thing. Just hop. Hop.

89
00:09:22,144 --> 00:09:23,304
就是這樣 來吧！
That's it. Come on.

90
00:09:27,416 --> 00:09:29,976
里奇 夠了！ 我們認輸！
Ricky, enough! Enough!

91
00:09:30,086 --> 00:09:33,249
你的機器人被痛扁的聲音蓋過了你的聲音
I can't hear you over the sound of your robot being destroyed.

92
00:09:34,757 --> 00:09:36,850
殺了他！殺了他！殺了他！
Kill! Kill! Kill!

93
00:09:38,227 --> 00:09:39,387
快點 站起來！
Come on, get up.

94
00:09:40,363 --> 00:09:41,830
站起來！快點！
Get up! Come on!

95
00:09:45,368 --> 00:09:46,392
不要！
No!

96
00:09:50,439 --> 00:09:53,237
不要！不要！不要！
Come on, no. No, no, no!

97
00:09:59,448 --> 00:10:03,043
各位先生女士們 讓我們為我們的勇士喝彩吧！
Ladies and gentlemen, let's hear it for our warriors out here today

98
00:10:03,152 --> 00:10:05,848
就在今天 就在我們的圣蘭卓鄉村市集
at the 2020 San Leandro County Fair.

99
00:10:05,955 --> 00:10:07,889
感謝你們的參觀
Thank you for coming out,

100
00:10:07,990 --> 00:10:11,721
我保證下次會更精彩的
and we'll see you next time, because there will be one.

101
00:10:12,762 --> 00:10:13,786
把腳還給我
Give me that leg.

102
00:10:13,896 --> 00:10:15,796
可以 要五塊錢
Sure. For five dollars.

103
00:10:15,898 --> 00:10:17,490
活該 ！
Boo-yah!

104
00:10:19,402 --> 00:10:24,169
各位先生女士們 很好 不可思議的好玩對吧？
All right! That was ridiculous fun, now wasn't it, ladies and gentlemen?

105
00:10:25,274 --> 00:10:28,766
Charlie男孩 等下我來拿錢 你最好準備好！
I'm going to come by for my money, Charlie boy. You best have it.

106
00:10:28,878 --> 00:10:30,937
- 大家一起喊 "嗨！" - 嗨！
- Everybody say "hey!" - Hey!

107
00:10:31,047 --> 00:10:34,847
- 大家一起喊 "喝！" - 喝！
- Everybody say "ho!" - Ho!

108
00:10:34,950 --> 00:10:38,147
拽不起來了吧？哈哈！小機器人！
How about that? How you doing there, little robot?

109
00:10:54,904 --> 00:10:56,462
我的鑰匙 他媽的！
My keys, damn it.

110
00:10:57,339 --> 00:10:59,364
再靠近一步 我就狠狠的扁你一頓
One more step and I'll drop you like your girlfriend.

111
00:10:59,475 --> 00:11:00,874
Charlie 不要緊張
Charlie, relax.

112
00:11:00,976 --> 00:11:03,877
我不會付錢 那是不公平的比賽 甚至花了我最后一個機器人！
I'm not paying you. That was a bogus fight. It cost me my last robot.

113
00:11:03,979 --> 00:11:06,846
- 讓我們先說 - 你還記得卡洛琳法羅嗎？
- Just listen to us. - Do you recall Caroline Fallon?

114
00:11:07,450 --> 00:11:10,419
她是我的前女友 我已經十年沒見過她了 她想干嘛？
She's my ex-girlfriend. I haven't seen her in ten years. What does she want?

115
00:11:10,519 --> 00:11:12,248
她死了
Nothing. She died.

116
00:11:13,055 --> 00:11:14,488
你還記不記得Max
Do you recall Max Kenton?

117
00:11:16,258 --> 00:11:18,123
他是我兒子 他應該已經九歲了
He's my son. He's got to be nine.

118
00:11:18,227 --> 00:11:19,956
- 十一歲 - 十一歲 好吧！
- Eleven. - Eleven. OK.

119
00:11:21,464 --> 00:11:22,954
他也死了？
Is he dead, too?

120
00:11:23,065 --> 00:11:25,898
不 他還好好的 所以我們才來
No, he's fine. That's why we're here.

121
00:11:30,148 --> 00:11:33,148
翻譯：閑閑的猛男 校對：目前沒有

122
00:11:52,094 --> 00:11:55,894
今天法庭要判決Max 十一歲
This court is convened to address the custodial status

123
00:11:55,998 --> 00:11:58,262
他的監護權的所屬
of one Max Kenton, age 11.

124
00:11:58,367 --> 00:12:02,997
母親是剛過世的卡洛琳法羅 父親是Charlie肯頓
Mother, Caroline Fallon, deceased. Father, Charles Kenton.

125
00:12:03,105 --> 00:12:05,130
黛博拉 法羅 巴恩 你是小男孩的阿姨嗎？
Debra Fallon Barnes, you're the boy's aunt.

126
00:12:05,241 --> 00:12:10,543
是的 就像我所表達的 我的先生 馬文 他很健康
Yes. As I've already told you, my husband, Marvin, is wealthy,

127
00:12:10,846 --> 00:12:14,213
我們可以好好的照顧Max 
and we can more than provide for Max.

128
00:12:14,316 --> 00:12:17,843
我認為這樣很好 但是根據德州的法律
I appreciate that, but per Texas state law, without a written will

129
00:12:17,953 --> 00:12:19,887
如果他沒出席的生父Charlie肯頓
next of kin retains custody.

130
00:12:19,989 --> 00:12:23,152
沒有放棄他的撫養權的話
Charles Kenton, who is aware of this custody hearing,

131
00:12:23,259 --> 00:12:24,556
我們還在等他出席
and we are expecting him...

132
00:12:24,860 --> 00:12:27,294
我要一個新的機器人
I need a new robot now.

133
00:12:27,396 --> 00:12:29,887
我幫突擊者在下周六安排一場大比賽
I had a big fight for Ambush next Saturday.

134
00:12:29,999 --> 00:12:31,296
我現在要趕去處理一件事
I got to show up with something.

135
00:12:31,400 --> 00:12:36,303
大聲公要賣嗎？大聲公是殺手級的！
Noisy Boy is for sale? In his day, Noisy Boy was a killer.

136
00:12:36,405 --> 00:12:39,101
多少錢？很劃算 有沒有其他的毛病？
How much? That's a good deal. What's wrong with him?

137
00:12:40,209 --> 00:12:41,471
我要買
I can live with that.

138
00:12:42,912 --> 00:12:44,277
但是我現在沒有錢
I don't have it.

139
00:12:44,380 --> 00:12:48,441
Charlie肯頓在Max一出生的時候就沒有盡到父親的義務
Charles Kenton waived all of his rights to custody right after the boy was born.

140
00:12:48,551 --> 00:12:51,179
我們可以更好地照顧Max
I can more than provide for Max.

141
00:12:53,422 --> 00:12:54,616
你是Charlie肯頓嗎？
Please be Charles Kenton.

142
00:12:57,426 --> 00:12:59,257
是的 就是Charlie
Charlie, yeah.

143
00:13:00,563 --> 00:13:02,997
我來簽一些文件 放棄一些權力
I'm here to sign some paper that releases my rights

144
00:13:03,098 --> 00:13:05,066
放棄我小孩的監護權
to the custody of my son.

145
00:13:05,167 --> 00:13:07,101
所以我才來 我是應該來吧？
That's why I'm here. Do I need to be here?

146
00:13:07,203 --> 00:13:08,465
Charlie
Charlie.

147
00:13:09,505 --> 00:13:10,995
你還記得我嗎？
Do you even remember me?

148
00:13:11,941 --> 00:13:14,307
- 黛博拉 卡洛琳的妹妹 - 是哦 黛博拉 你還好嗎？
- Debra, Caroline's sister. - Yeah, Debra. How are you?

149
00:13:14,410 --> 00:13:16,344
肯頓先生 請坐！
Mr. Kenton. Please take a seat.

150
00:13:19,882 --> 00:13:22,942
法官大人 我可以先去看看我的外甥嗎？
Your Honor, may I please go and see my nephew now?

151
00:13:23,052 --> 00:13:24,076
可以！請去吧！
Yes, you may.

152
00:13:24,186 --> 00:13:25,983
- 你呢？肯頓先生！ - 什么？
- How about you, Mr. Kenton? - What?

153
00:13:26,088 --> 00:13:28,522
如果你想要 你可以跟你兒子獨處一會兒！
You can spend some time with him, if you'd like.

154
00:13:28,624 --> 00:13:30,353
- 跟我兒子？- 是的 你兒子！
- With the kid? - Yeah, the kid.

155
00:13:30,459 --> 00:13:32,359
