當然 讓我們一起到拳王的貴賓室
Sure. Yeah. Let's head up to the champ's suite. Sure.

941
01:16:33,271 --> 01:16:34,363
哇
Wow.

942
01:16:34,673 --> 01:16:38,473
- 先生們 我是法羅 蘭蔻娃 - 你好 我是Charlie肯頓 這是...
- Gentlemen, I'm Farra Lemkova. - Yeah. I'm Charlie Kenton, and...

943
01:16:38,777 --> 01:16:40,768
當然還有松本先生
And this, of course, is Tak Mashido.

944
01:16:40,879 --> 01:16:43,143
老天爺！是松本先生
Holy shit. It's Tak Mashido.

945
01:16:44,149 --> 01:16:47,380
我知道你們今晚有一場重要的比賽 所以我就直接了當說了
I know you have a very important fight tonight, so I'll get right to it.

946
01:16:47,686 --> 01:16:51,122
那個動作我喜歡 很漂亮的動作 所以... (Charlie已經語無倫次了）
It's a little far from the action for my liking. It's nice. I like it, though.

947
01:16:51,223 --> 01:16:55,159
漂亮的相片... 哇！非常漂亮
Very nicely... Wow. That's a great shot.

948
01:16:55,260 --> 01:16:57,421
看看這個 你要個簽名嗎？你介意嗎？
Look at that. You want an autograph? Would you mind?

949
01:16:57,729 --> 01:16:59,458
我想買你們的機器人
I'd like to buy your robot.

950
01:17:01,800 --> 01:17:06,100
他對我們是一個很好的前場表演機器人 所以我愿意付你們
He'd be useful sparring bot for Zeus. And for that I'm willing to pay.

951
01:17:07,139 --> 01:17:10,233
二十萬
$200,000.

952
01:17:10,342 --> 01:17:11,900
- 沒問題 - 我不要賣
- Done. - He's not for sale.

953
01:17:12,010 --> 01:17:14,740
- 當然要 我們絕對可以... - Atom是不賣的
- Of course he is. We can definitely... - He's not for sale.

954
01:17:15,347 --> 01:17:20,341
你們還有十五分鐘要對上雙子星
You are 15 minutes away from getting in the ring with Twin Cities,

955
01:17:20,452 --> 01:17:22,386
一個邪惡的職業機器人
a vicious League bot.

956
01:17:22,487 --> 01:17:27,925
所以我的報價在鈴聲前才有效
So, to be clear, my offer stands until the starting bell.

957
01:17:28,026 --> 01:17:32,190
好的 但是讓我再說一遍 不賣！
OK. And just to be clear, he's not for sale!

958
01:17:32,297 --> 01:17:34,424
現在不賣 以后也不賣
Not now, not ever.

959
01:17:35,767 --> 01:17:37,928
給我一分鐘想清楚 好嗎！
Give me a minute to clear this up, OK?

960
01:17:38,437 --> 01:17:40,928
松本 你好嗎？Max！！慢一點！
Tak, how are you? Max!

961
01:17:43,375 --> 01:17:45,366
聰明一點 我知道你很喜歡他
Be smart. I know you love him,

962
01:17:45,477 --> 01:17:48,071
但是過二十分鐘 它可能就毀了
but in 20 minutes there may be nothing left to love.

963
01:17:48,180 --> 01:17:51,274
- 考慮一下 接受吧！ - 你動動頭腦想一下
- Think about it. Take the offer. - You think about it.

964
01:17:52,017 --> 01:17:55,509
他們為什么要賣Atom？因為他是與眾不同的
Why does she want Atom? Because he's different from other bots!

965
01:17:55,821 --> 01:17:57,789
是啊 是不一樣 是小個 虛弱的
Yeah, he's different. He's smaller, weaker,

966
01:17:57,889 --> 01:18:00,016
- 而且他會被揍的很慘的 - 他是拳擊手
- and he's going to get his ass kicked. - He's a boxer.

967
01:18:00,192 --> 01:18:02,422
我們叫他拳擊 你教他拳擊
We taught him to box. You taught him to box!

968
01:18:03,161 --> 01:18:05,129
- 這個就是它的價值 - 我也是這么認為
- That's worth something. - I think it is, too.

969
01:18:05,230 --> 01:18:08,893
我想這個值20萬 20萬大元
I think it's worth 200 grand. Two hundred grand.

970
01:18:09,000 --> 01:18:11,969
我們可以整晚都在這里兜
We can go round and round this all night long.

971
01:18:12,070 --> 01:18:13,367
看著我
Look at me.

972
01:18:14,773 --> 01:18:16,070
但是絕對不會賣的
But it's not going to happen.

973
01:18:17,209 --> 01:18:18,506
對不起我還有比賽
I got a fight to get to.

974
01:18:33,158 --> 01:18:37,060
各位先生女士們 今晚...
Ladies and gentlemen, tonight,

975
01:18:37,162 --> 01:18:41,929
即將帶來的 鋼鐵擂臺冠軍杯
the march towards the Real Steel Championship

976
01:18:42,033 --> 01:18:45,093
來到了底特律
makes its way through Detroit's

977
01:18:45,203 --> 01:18:49,264
維吉尼亞州 史倍狀中心
Virgin America Spectrum!

978
01:18:53,245 --> 01:18:57,579
開始我們的第一輪排名賽
Kicking off the evening, in our first undercard,

979
01:18:57,883 --> 01:19:00,613
二個頭的暴君
the two-headed tyrant,

980
01:19:00,919 --> 01:19:05,151
雙子星
Twin Cities!

981
01:19:35,554 --> 01:19:40,890
對手是第一次參加職業比賽的
Opposing Twin Cities, in his first professional fight,

982
01:19:40,992 --> 01:19:44,450
讓我們一起喊
hailing from parts unknown,

983
01:19:44,563 --> 01:19:46,326
Atom
Atom!

984
01:20:42,053 --> 01:20:43,452
- 跳得好 老板 - 謝謝
- Nice work, boss. - Thanks.

985
01:20:43,555 --> 01:20:45,420
- 你切換到戰斗模式了？- 當然
- Did you switch him to fight mode? - Of course.

986
01:20:45,523 --> 01:20:48,287
- 雙子星是訓練來撕裂對手 - Atom 也可以
- This bot is tough to put down. - Atom can do it.

987
01:20:49,261 --> 01:20:52,287
看看那里 那二個握著搖桿在熒幕后面的怪胎
Look over there. You see those geeks with the joysticks and consoles?

988
01:20:52,397 --> 01:20:54,194
他們完全控制他們的機器人
They're controlling everything their bot does.

989
01:20:54,299 --> 01:20:55,459
他們隨時監看它的系統
They're monitoring his systems,

990
01:20:55,567 --> 01:20:58,161
隨時調整他的戰術
seeing what he sees, stadium feeds of the fights.

991
01:20:58,270 --> 01:21:00,329
這個不是以前我們對戰的地下那種用遙控器的級別
This is not like the underground handheld remote bots

992
01:21:00,438 --> 01:21:02,338
這是職業賽 你要了解到
we've been fighting. This is the League. Stand on that.

993
01:21:02,440 --> 01:21:04,408
那我們要怎么做？
So what do we do?

994
01:21:05,176 --> 01:21:08,668
我們要聰明一點 有耐心 然后祈禱
We fight smart, we be patient. And pray.

995
01:21:10,248 --> 01:21:12,045
正經一點 不是那種祈禱
Seriously, pray.

996
01:21:14,519 --> 01:21:15,543
準備好！
Ready!

997
01:21:16,688 --> 01:21:18,553
- 準備好了 - 手舉起來
- Ready! - Hands up.

998
01:21:18,657 --> 01:21:21,091
拳手準備好了！ 開始！
Fighters ready! Fight!

999
01:21:24,663 --> 01:21:26,028
交戰開始
Engage.

1000
01:21:27,265 --> 01:21:32,396
滑動！ 右邊！ 退后 右 左 左 掩護好
Slip! Right! Lean back. Right, left! Cover up!

1001
01:21:35,540 --> 01:21:37,030
低頭 左勾拳
Duck! Left roundhouse!

1002
01:21:39,678 --> 01:21:41,145
該死的
Damn it.

1003
01:21:48,420 --> 01:21:52,151
閃左邊！ 閃右邊！防守好！
Lean left! Lean right! Cover up! Cover up!

1004
01:21:52,257 --> 01:21:55,192
- 發生什么事了？- 他要對上太多頭了
- What's going on in there? - He's taking too many hits.

1005
01:22:01,099 --> 01:22:02,327
把手舉起來
Get your hands up!

1006
01:22:05,203 --> 01:22:07,068
離開角落！ 移動！
Get out of that corner! Move!

1007
01:22:10,108 --> 01:22:12,474
他在被狠狠修理了 趕快告訴他怎么做！
He's getting killed in there! Tell him what to do!

1008
01:22:12,577 --> 01:22:15,410
對手有二個頭 二個頭都對著我們 而且沒有盲點
That guy's got two heads, a foot of reach on us, and no blind spot.

1009
01:22:15,513 --> 01:22:17,378
對手一定有弱點 找出來吧！
He's got to have a weakness. Find it!

1010
01:22:23,355 --> 01:22:24,583
看到了 等一下 看到了！
Wait, wait, wait.

1011
01:22:25,323 --> 01:22:28,224
右手肩膀 右手肩膀 他有一個習慣動作
Right shoulder, right shoulder, right shoulder! He's got a tell!

1012
01:22:28,326 --> 01:22:30,760
每次出右拳的時候 他都有一個準備動作
He's got a hitch in his shoulder every time he throws that right bomb!

1013
01:22:31,062 --> 01:22:33,223
抓到了 看到沒？又有準備動作了
We got him! See? Here it comes again!

1014
01:22:33,331 --> 01:22:36,095
低頭！ 旋轉！ 滑到左邊！ 繞一圈！ 一 二！
Duck! Spin! Slide left! Roundhouse! One, two!

1015
01:22:36,201 --> 01:22:39,398
退后 退后一步 滑到左邊！
Backstep. Backstep. Backstep. Lean right.

1016
01:22:39,504 --> 01:22:41,529
來吧 Charlie 跟上去！
Come on, Charlie! Get in there!

1017
01:22:41,639 --> 01:22:44,233
我們要縮近到對我們有利的距離
Got to get in close where he can't use that size and reach on us!

1018
01:22:44,342 --> 01:22:47,505
攻擊左邊身體 右邊身體 再左邊身體
Left to the body! Right to the body! Left to the body!

1019
01:22:47,612 --> 01:22:49,102
耶 有作用了！
Yeah, it's working!

1020
01:22:49,214 --> 01:22:51,114
繼續低一點的姿勢 左 右 左
Stay downstairs! Left, right, left!

1021
01:22:52,550 --> 01:22:55,417
- 這個模式沒有用 - 左 右勾 滑動
- These program modes aren't working. - Left! Right hook, slip!

1022
01:22:55,520 --> 01:22:59,183
右上鉤拳！ 左上鉤全！躲左邊 閃右邊
Right uppercut! Left uppercut! Duck left. Counter right!

1023
01:22:59,290 --> 01:23:01,850
- 打到他 Atom！ - 看看Charlie的絕招
- Get him, Atom! - Here comes the Charlie Special.

1024
01:23:02,160 --> 01:23:05,129
三連擊攻擊身體！ 外面！ 里面！ 反向！
Three-punch combo to the body! Out! In! Counter!

1025
01:23:05,230 --> 01:23:07,130
- 一二一連擊！ - 一二一連擊！
- Two-one-two! - Two-one-two.

1026
01:23:07,232 --> 01:23:08,665
盯住他 ！ 前后分身 ！
Stay on him! Lunging right!

1027
01:23:11,536 --> 01:23:14,266
你要讓他逃走右拳攻擊身體！ 右直拳打頭！
Don't let him go. Right to the body! Straight right to the head!

1028
01:23:19,244 --> 01:23:20,711
系統崩潰了！
We got a systems crash!

1029
01:23:20,812 --> 01:23:22,336
打倒他 Atom！
Get him, Atom!

1030
01:23:25,517 --> 01:23:26,814
怎么可能發生這種事？
This is not happening, man.

1031
01:23:27,118 --> 01:23:29,313
- 打倒他 Charlie！ - 左旋轉
- Put him away, Charlie! - Spin left!

1032
01:23:30,321 --> 01:23:31,583
右旋轉
Spin right!

1033
01:23:33,792 --> 01:23:34,816
干掉他
Finish him!

1034
01:23:35,126 --> 01:23:37,151
- 就是現在 - 右勾拳
- Do it! - Right uppercut!

1035
01:23:47,372 --> 01:23:48,464
倒了！
He's down!

1036
01:23:49,441 --> 01:23:52,740
1！2！3！
One! Two! Three!

1037
01:23:52,844 --> 01:23:55,745
4！5！6！
Four! Five! Six!

1038
01:23:55,847 --> 01:23:57,838
我們干掉他了 準備好！
We got him. Stay down!

1039
01:24:00,351 --> 01:24:01,750
結束比賽 擊倒！
He's out! He's out!

1040
01:24:07,725 --> 01:24:08,817
耶！
Yeah!

1041
01:24:11,796 --> 01:24:13,627
回來！
Corner!

1042
01:24:13,731 --> 01:24:16,723
回到角落來！
Corner! Corner.

1043
01:24:18,436 --> 01:24:19,630
勝利！
Victory!

1044
01:24:20,839 --> 01:24:25,173
在一分47秒...
In a time of one minute, 47 seconds

1045
01:24:25,276 --> 01:24:27,642
第一回合......
of the first round,

1046
01:24:27,745 --> 01:24:29,474
Atom擊敗了...
Atom has defeat...

1047
01:24:30,582 --> 01:24:33,380
感謝各位今天晚上的觀看
I want to thank everyone for coming out tonight!

1048
01:24:35,920 --> 01:24:40,220
我們從垃圾場來的的小巨人 擊倒了職業級的機器人
Our little bot from the junkyard got a shot at a League fight.

1049
01:24:40,325 --> 01:24:41,622
爽不爽？
How about that?

1050
01:24:42,827 --> 01:24:47,491
最后我要對一個背地里操作的女孩說...
And the last thing I want to say to a special girl who won't be named,

1051
01:24:47,599 --> 01:24:49,499
法羅 蘭蔻娃
Farra Lemkova.

1052
01:24:53,805 --> 01:24:57,571
她想買我的機器人 用你們的錢來操作比賽
That instead of buying my robot, using your money to control this sport...

1053
01:24:57,675 --> 01:24:59,506
- 就是她 - 不是我說的
- That's it! - I'm not done.

1054
01:24:59,611 --> 01:25:02,239
你為什么不給小巨人一個最大的機會？
Why not give the littlest guy the biggest shot?

1055
01:25:02,747 --> 01:25:06,649
因為我敢打賭 你不敢給我們這個機會
Because I bet if you give him a shot, he'll surprise you!

1056
01:25:06,751 --> 01:25:08,343
大家想不想看小巨人
Wouldn't you like to see a little guy

1057
01:25:08,453 --> 01:25:10,478
對抗聯盟冠軍
get a shot at the Real Steel Championship?

1058
01:25:14,492 --> 01:25:17,928
我要挑戰宙斯！
I challenge Zeus to a fight.

1059
01:25:19,964 --> 01:25:23,957
任何時間 任何地點！
Any time, any place, anywhere!

1060
01:25:24,269 --> 01:25:27,261
告訴我們 ！ 我們就來！
You name it! We will be there!

1061
01:25:34,913 --> 01:25:36,881
我來為各位安排這場比賽
I'm going to get us that fight!

1062
01:25:40,785 --> 01:25:43,811
Atom Atom Atom...
Atom, Atom, Atom...

1063
01:25:56,701 --> 01:25:58,965
那是很沒腦的舉動 你就這樣挑戰宙斯？
That was a ballsy move, you challenging Zeus like that.

1064
01:25:59,270 --> 01:26:00,635
那只是一時的沖動
That's one thing to call it.

1065
01:26:00,738 --> 01:26:02,000
很多人會很想看的
A lot of people would like to see that.

1066
01:26:02,307 --> 01:26:05,003
- 是的 大家都想 - 聽這個小鬼說的 天啊！
- You're damn right they would. - You listening to this kid? Jeez!

1067
01:26:05,310 --> 01:26:07,005
- 好比賽 兄弟 - 謝謝你
- Good fight, fellas. - Thanks, man.

1068
01:26:07,312 --> 01:26:08,973
- 看看這個 慶祝一下 - 耶
- Look at this. Let's celebrate. - Yeah.

1069
01:26:09,280 --> 01:26:12,408
- 好吧 7-3分賬 對不對？- 耶 我7你3
- All right, 70-30, right? - Yeah, 70 for me and 30 for you.

1070
01:26:12,517 --> 01:26:14,007
- 對對對 - 很好笑！
- That's so right. - That's very funny.

1071
01:26:14,319 --> 01:26:18,380
- 我就說我們不應該賣掉它 - 喔 喔 喔！
- I told you we shouldn't have sold him. - OK. No, no, no.

1072
01:26:18,489 --> 01:26:22,653
我想起來了 誰才對？說啊 說出來“Max是對的”？
I remember now. Who's right? Say who's right. Say "Max is right."

1073
01:26:22,760 --> 01:26:24,728
好啦好啦 你才是對的！
All right, all right. All right.

1074
01:26:24,829 --> 01:26:28,424
- 我們合作無間是吧 - 不是不是 要說“Max是對的”
- We're a good team. - No, no. Max is right.

1075
01:26:28,666 --> 01:26:30,964
不敢相信 這么多錢 感謝你 雙子星！
That was unbelievable. Thank you, Twin Cities.

1076
01:26:33,438 --> 01:26:34,871
- 收好了？- 耶
- We set? - Yeah.

1077
01:26:34,973 --> 01:26:37,339
- 我們去慶祝了！ - Charlie男孩
- Let's do it. - Charlie boy.

1078
01:26:38,309 --> 01:26:41,608
- 里奇 我才正想要打給你 - 噢？是嗎？
- Ricky, I was just going to call you. - Oh, yeah.

1079
01:26:41,713 --> 01:26:44,580
我是真的打算打給你
I actually really was going to call you.

1080
01:26:44,716 --> 01:26:46,513
沒事 不用在意
Don't worry about that.

1081
01:26:46,618 --> 01:26:48,643
真的是了不起的比賽！
That was a heck of a fight.

1082
01:26:48,753 --> 01:26:51,017
恭喜二位 真的是太好了！
Congratulations to both of you. That was good.

1083
01:26:51,322 --> 01:26:54,018
真的是了不起的戰斗 干得好 小朋友
It was an amazing fight. That was a great job, young man.

1084
01:26:54,993 --> 01:26:56,483
- 來吧！兄弟 - 干嘛？
- Come on, man. - What?

1085
01:26:56,594 --> 01:27:00,724
- 你不會是說真的吧？- 你以為我在開玩笑？
- You serious? - You thought I was joking

1086
01:27:00,832 --> 01:27:02,629
我說“見你一次就海扁你一次”
when I said I'd beat you within an inch of your life?

1087
01:27:02,734 --> 01:27:05,828
你以為我是開玩笑？告訴你 絕對不是！
He thought that was a joke. It wasn't a joke.

1088
01:27:05,937 --> 01:27:10,101
我小孩在這里 我也準備錢要給你了 不要這樣
I got a kid here. And I have your money. We don't have a problem.

1089
01:27:10,408 --> 01:27:12,933
我看你也不敢
I'm sure you do,

1090
01:27:13,044 --> 01:27:16,070
但是不只是因為錢是吧？你都知道的
but I think we know it's about much more than money, don't we?

1091
01:27:16,381 --> 01:27:21,546
好的 你要多少？二萬 二萬五 三萬夠不夠？
All right. What do you want? You want 25, 30? You want 30 grand?

1092
01:27:21,653 --> 01:27:23,416
- 我手頭上有現金 - 是哦！對啊
- I got the money in cash here. - Yeah, right.

1093
01:27:23,521 --> 01:27:26,649
趕快跑！Max 跑 快跑！
Let's go! Max, go! Go, go! Run!

1094
01:27:26,758 --> 01:27:30,057
- 趕快跑 跟上 快！ - 趕快抓住他！
- Run! Come on. Keep up, keep up! - Get him now!

1095
01:27:30,361 --> 01:27:31,623
跑 快！
Run! Come on!

1096
01:27:33,498 --> 01:27:35,125
放開他！放開他！
Get off him! Get off him!

1097
01:27:38,569 --> 01:27:39,593
過來！
Come here!

1098
01:27:43,908 --> 01:27:45,000
嗨 里奇！
Hey, Ricky.

1099
01:27:45,109 --> 01:27:46,770
那是他的錢 跟他無關
That's his money! Leave him out of this!

1100
01:27:59,090 --> 01:28:01,081
停
Stop!

1101
01:28:03,594 --> 01:28:04,856
停！
Stop!

1102
01:28:04,962 --> 01:28:08,591
把所有的錢都拿走 全拿走！
Take all his money. Take it all.

1103
01:28:11,102 --> 01:28:13,662
小朋友 你的朋友是個人渣
Your friend's a real dirt bag, kid.

1104
01:28:13,771 --> 01:28:15,432
他是我父親
He's my father!

1105
01:28:17,575 --> 01:28:22,410
看來可以少扁你一次了
Well. Looks like a little less than an inch of your life.

1106
01:28:22,513 --> 01:28:25,175
嗯 好好的給你上一課
Well, buddy, that will teach him.

1107
01:28:30,822 --> 01:28:33,757
就像以前一樣 Charlie男孩
Just like old times, Charlie boy!

1108
01:28:33,858 --> 01:28:35,120
走吧 兄弟們
Let's go, boys.

1109
01:29:01,052 --> 01:29:05,182
對不起 Max 我很抱歉
I'm sorry, Max. I'm sorry. Sorry.

1110
01:29:45,830 --> 01:29:47,661
- 我們來這里做什么？- Max 只是...
- What are we doing here? - Max, just...

1111
01:29:47,765 --> 01:29:50,859
來找法羅？她是不是打給你了？我們要跟宙斯比賽了？
Is it Farra? She called you, didn't she? We're going to get the Zeus fight.

1112
01:29:50,968 --> 01:29:55,132
不是宙斯 我想了很多 然后......
It's not the Zeus people. I've been thinking about all this, and...

1113
01:29:57,175 --> 01:29:58,267
Max
Max!

1114
01:30:07,985 --> 01:30:09,816
很高興見到你
It's so good to see you.

1115
01:30:09,921 --> 01:30:12,515
- 為什么她在這里？- 你最好還是現在跟她回去
- What is she doing here? - It's better if you go with her now.

1116
01:30:12,623 --> 01:30:14,682
我們被痛扁了 所以你打電話給她來接我？
We get beat up, so you call her to come and get me?

1117
01:30:14,792 --> 01:30:16,692
他被打了 我就說他沒法照顧好Max的！
He's been beat up. I told you he couldn't take care of him!

1118
01:30:16,794 --> 01:30:19,592
是的 我打給他們 你看我們 真是一團糟
Yeah. I called her. Look at us. We're a mess.

1119
01:30:19,697 --> 01:30:21,722
我們很好 叫他們走
We're fine. She can leave!

1120
01:30:21,833 --> 01:30:24,859
Atom打得很好 我們可以把錢再賺回來
Atom's fighting good. We can make the money back.

1121
01:30:25,670 --> 01:30:27,570
Charlie 拜托！
Charlie, please.

1122
01:30:28,606 --> 01:30:29,698
只是...
Just...

1123
01:30:32,610 --> 01:30:35,078
Charlie 我們過得很好
Charlie, we're doing so good.

1124
01:30:37,014 --> 01:30:38,982
Charlie 拜托 不要
Charlie, please, no.

1125
01:30:40,251 --> 01:30:42,913
不要 不要 不要
Don't. Don't. Don't.

1126
01:30:43,921 --> 01:30:46,856
拜托 拜托
Please. Please.

1127
01:30:51,529 --> 01:30:54,623
相信我 這樣對你比較好 好嗎？
Trust me, kid. It's better this way, all right?

1128
01:30:55,266 --> 01:30:58,133
你以為這樣對我比較好 其實不是的
I know you think you know what's right, but you don't.

1129
01:30:58,236 --> 01:30:59,897
你還年輕 你不懂
You're too young. You don't know.

1130
01:31:00,004 --> 01:31:01,665
看著我 相信我！
Look at me, trust me.

1131
01:31:01,772 --> 01:31:05,003
而且法律上 她有你的監護權 我還能怎么做？
And legally she has custody, so what can I do?

1132
01:31:05,977 --> 01:31:07,808
我還能做什么？
What can I do?

1133
01:31:23,060 --> 01:31:24,755
我不要你的錢 馬文
I don't want your money, Marvin.

1134
01:31:25,863 --> 01:31:27,956
Max 我們有自己的游泳池哦
Max, we have our own swimming pool

1135
01:31:28,065 --> 01:31:32,764
而且我們有按摩浴缸 還有很多好玩的玩具給你玩
and we have a hot tub and a lot of super fun toys to play with.

1136
01:31:32,870 --> 01:31:35,634
你要玩玩嘛？很好玩的哦
Do you want to play with them? It's going to be fun.

1137
01:31:36,340 --> 01:31:37,830
情況如何？
What's going on?

1138
01:31:37,942 --> 01:31:40,706
謝謝你 他根本不跟我講話
He won't even talk to me, so thanks for that, Charlie.

1139
01:31:41,746 --> 01:31:43,179
我先到車子里面等
I'm going to wait in the car.

1140
01:31:45,883 --> 01:31:48,351
你不想講話？好 我說
You don't want to talk, fine. I'll talk.

1141
01:31:48,653 --> 01:31:50,621
你要我說什么？我很抱歉？
What do you want me to say? I'm sorry?

1142
01:31:50,721 --> 01:31:53,781
從一開始就是這樣
You knew from day one what this was.

1143
01:31:53,891 --> 01:31:55,756
從你開始決定上車就是這樣
You decided to take the ride.

1144
01:31:56,260 --> 01:32:00,128
你以為我可以跟你那個破爛堆撿到...
You thought me, you, and a little robot from the junk heap

1145
01:32:00,298 --> 01:32:02,789
的破機器人一起坐著看夕陽？
were going to ride off into the sunset?

1146
01:32:04,835 --> 01:32:07,235
你看錯我了
No, you forgot who I was!

1147
01:32:13,311 --> 01:32:14,801
你應該過的好一點的生活...
You deserve better...

1148
01:32:16,213 --> 01:32:17,305
...比我還好
than me.

1149
01:32:21,886 --> 01:32:23,683
拜托說幾句話吧？
Will you say something, please?

1150
01:32:23,788 --> 01:32:26,222
我努力過了 你還要我怎么做？
I tried. What do you want from me?

1151
01:32:26,324 --> 01:32:28,087
我要你為我奮斗
I want you to fight for me.

1152
01:32:29,293 --> 01:32:31,158
這就是我想要的
That's all I ever wanted.

1153
01:32:32,408 --> 01:32:35,408
翻譯：閑閑的猛男 校對：目前沒有

1154
01:34:36,320 --> 01:34:37,810
不要問
Don't ask.

1155
01:34:39,924 --> 01:34:41,357
Max走了？
So no Max.

1156
01:34:42,760 --> 01:34:46,355
最好的安排 馬文及黛博拉他們有錢 會好好照顧Max
It's better this way. Marv and Debra have money. Max is set.

1157
01:34:46,464 --> 01:34:48,295
你有沒有看到他看你的樣子？
Did you not see the way he looked at you?

1158
01:34:49,467 --> 01:34:51,799
就像我看我爹的樣子
That's the way I looked at my dad.

1159
01:34:51,902 --> 01:34:54,097
我多想再重溫那種感覺
Even now I would give anything to have that back.

1160
01:34:54,205 --> 01:34:58,266
你父親不一樣 他從一開始就跟你在一起
Your dad was special. He was in your corner from day one.

1161
01:34:59,243 --> 01:35:01,040
我 我早就搞砸了
Me, come on. I blew it.

1162
01:35:02,947 --> 01:35:04,312
我搞砸了
I blew it.

1163
01:35:05,216 --> 01:35:07,150
當Max出生的時候...
When Max was born I just...

1164
01:35:07,852 --> 01:35:09,251
...我嚇傻了
freaked out.

1165
01:35:09,353 --> 01:35:11,548
你沒有感到滿足嗎？
But something would have been better than nothing.

1166
01:35:11,856 --> 01:35:13,118
不對 是手足無措
I wouldn't know where to start.

1167
01:35:13,224 --> 01:35:14,248
- 我不滿足 - 不 你很幸福
- Yeah, you do. - I don't.

1168
01:35:14,358 --> 01:35:15,985
- 你是的 - 不是
- You do. - No.

1169
01:35:16,961 --> 01:35:18,053
你是的
You do.

1170
01:35:50,995 --> 01:35:52,087
我要走了
I got to go.

1171
01:35:55,132 --> 01:35:56,599
開了1200英里就為了這個吻？
Twelve hundred miles for a kiss.

1172
01:35:58,202 --> 01:36:00,602
值得 值得！
Worth it. Worth it.

1173
01:36:12,049 --> 01:36:13,539
去找他 Charlie！
Go get him, Charlie.

1174
01:36:17,021 --> 01:36:18,386
你說得好像你爹的口氣
You sound like your dad.

1175
01:36:46,617 --> 01:36:50,451
我知道你認為我遺棄了你
Look, I know you think I abandoned you,

1176
01:36:50,554 --> 01:36:53,421
而且我還真的這樣做了
and I guess I did originally.

1177
01:36:53,524 --> 01:36:54,548
你還賣掉我
Then you sold me.

1178
01:36:55,259 --> 01:36:56,385
Charlie？
Charlie.

1179
01:36:57,461 --> 01:36:59,429
這個地方一點都不歡迎你
You have no business being here.

1180
01:36:59,530 --> 01:37:02,090
沒錯 你有全部的監護權 他是你的
That's true. You've got full custody. He's yours.

1181
01:37:02,199 --> 01:37:06,135
而且我知道所有的事都是我的錯 但是請你讓我...
And I know I've done all kinds of wrong by this kid, but if you'll let me...

1182
01:37:08,205 --> 01:37:10,230
...我想要做一些補償
I'd just like to do one thing right.

1183
01:37:13,210 --> 01:37:14,268
好的
Right.

1184
01:37:15,946 --> 01:37:17,573
- 講到哪里了？- 你賣掉我
- Where were we? - You sold me.

1185
01:37:17,681 --> 01:37:19,979
哦 對了 耶 沒錯
Right, yeah, that happened.

1186
01:37:20,084 --> 01:37:22,279
- 等一下 什么？- 然后我們被痛扁一頓
- Wait, what? - Then we had our asses kicked.

1187
01:37:22,386 --> 01:37:24,547
然后你還要睡在一個破卡車里面
And you slept on a shelf in a truck, and it was awful.

1188
01:37:24,655 --> 01:37:26,384
- 很危險 - 非常危險
- And dangerous. - Really dangerous.

1189
01:37:26,490 --> 01:37:30,358
我知道 天啊 我真的很對不起你
I mean, I know. God. I'm sorry.

1190
01:37:31,428 --> 01:37:34,420
你來就是要說這個？就是要說你很抱歉？
That's why you came? To say you're sorry?

1191
01:37:34,531 --> 01:37:37,022
不 不止這些
No. I mean, yes. Yes.

1192
01:37:40,037 --> 01:37:43,598
我來還要再說 我了解了
But no. No, I came to tell you that I heard you.

1193
01:37:44,575 --> 01:37:48,067
我懂了 雖然我有一點遲鈍 但是我懂了
I got it. I'm a little slow, but I got it.

1194
01:37:49,513 --> 01:37:53,108
我知道我去流浪了 當你出生的時候
I know you had a bum ride, and I wasn't there and I should have been.

1195
01:37:54,351 --> 01:37:55,409
我實在不應該去的
I should have been.

1196
01:37:56,620 --> 01:37:58,144
你媽媽真的是...
Your mom was...

1197
01:37:58,656 --> 01:38:00,521
她很好是吧 很酷吧？
She was cool, wasn't she?

1198
01:38:02,092 --> 01:38:03,150
是的
She was.

1199
01:38:04,028 --> 01:38:05,325
她是最好的
She was the coolest.

1200
01:38:06,163 --> 01:38:08,688
耶 是的
Yeah, she was.

1201
01:38:11,568 --> 01:38:16,562
對她的事 我也很遺憾
And I'm sorry about... what happened with her.

1202
01:38:19,977 --> 01:38:22,605
馬克思 我沒法讓時間倒流
And I can't get those years back, Max,

1203
01:38:22,713 --> 01:38:26,012
但是現在我來了...
but I'm here right now...

1204
01:38:27,384 --> 01:38:30,649
...就像你看到的 我已經準備好要為你戰斗
and if you're up for it, I'm ready to fight.

1205
01:38:44,601 --> 01:38:46,330
跟宙斯的比賽安排好了
We got the Zeus fight.

1206
01:38:46,437 --> 01:38:47,597
真的？
What?

1207
01:38:47,705 --> 01:38:49,605
沒錯 安排好了
No, no, we didn't.

1208
01:38:50,507 --> 01:38:52,532
準備跟宙斯戰斗
You got the Zeus fight.

1209
01:38:56,447 --> 01:38:58,381
黛博拉 可以請你通融嗎？
So what do you say, Debra?

1210
01:38:58,482 --> 01:39:00,040
可不可以讓我們在一起奮戰 最后一次？
Can we do this one last thing?

1211
01:39:03,420 --> 01:39:06,048
- 就一晚 - 我們就這個小小要求
- One night. - It's all we need. Thank you.

1212
01:39:11,095 --> 01:39:14,724
我們很可能被痛宰 但是至少我們在一起奮斗
We'll probably get our asses kicked, but at least we'll go down swinging.

1213
01:39:15,599 --> 01:39:17,726
耶？你怎么決定？
Yeah? What do you say?

1214
01:39:20,037 --> 01:39:24,371
歡迎來到紐約的濱中心及觀看鋼鐵擂臺冠軍大賽
Welcome to New York's Bing Arena and the Real Steel Championship Bout.

1215
01:39:24,475 --> 01:39:26,773
提姆 這是場我們不敢想象會安排的比賽
Tim, it's the fight we never thought we'd see.

1216
01:39:27,077 --> 01:39:29,272
宙斯 永遠不敗的WRB拳王
Zeus, the undefeated WRB champion,

1217
01:39:29,380 --> 01:39:32,645
迎戰最近新崛起的初級的Atom
against the underdog, rising star Atom.

1218
01:39:32,750 --> 01:39:34,650
拳王的老板答應了這場比賽
The champ's handlers have agreed to fight

1219
01:39:34,752 --> 01:39:37,414
打破了聯盟循環賽的規則
outside the circle of well-known League bots,

1220
01:39:37,521 --> 01:39:41,651
而且準備給觀眾一場真正的重量級的對抗
and have decided to give the people a true David versus Goliath spectacle.

1221
01:39:41,759 --> 01:39:45,286
提姆 告訴我 拳王是不是腦袋進水了？
Now, Tim, help me out on this. Has the Zeus camp lost their mind?

1222
01:39:45,396 --> 01:39:47,159
有史以來最偉大的機器人格斗拳王
The greatest robot boxer of all time

1223
01:39:47,264 --> 01:39:50,256
為了跟一個第二代的 Atom 戰斗而交出他的腰帶？
gives a shot at the belt to a G-2 named Atom?

1224
01:39:50,367 --> 01:39:54,303
赫伯 如果你問松本先生 宙斯團隊是不是瘋了
Well, Herb, if you ask Tak Mashido, Team Zeus has lost their minds.

1225
01:39:54,405 --> 01:39:56,669
他可能會用一貫冷酷的表情回你
Now, he may look cool as he enters the arena,

1226
01:39:56,774 --> 01:39:59,800
然后用輕蔑的表情看待這場比賽
but he has made no bones about his disdain for this match up.

1227
01:40:00,110 --> 01:40:02,738
前幾天我們的攝影機試著要補抓這號表情
Our cameras tried to catch up with him earlier this week.

1228
01:40:02,846 --> 01:40:05,838
看看這個片段 松本先生甚至根本不想停下來跟媒體講話
Look at this clip. Mashido wouldn't even stop to talk to the press,

1229
01:40:06,150 --> 01:40:09,313
好像這場比賽是是侮辱了他偉大的創造物
referring only to this fight as an insult to his creation.

1230
01:40:09,420 --> 01:40:13,288
Charlie Atom的教練做的已經不只是跳級挑戰宙斯
Now, Max Kenton, Atom's trainer, did more than just challenge Zeus.

1231
01:40:13,390 --> 01:40:14,618
還是公開的挑戰
He did so publicly.

1232
01:40:14,725 --> 01:40:18,422
這個挑戰對拳王的公關形象是一個大挑戰
The challenge went viral and created a PR nightmare for the champ.

1233
01:40:18,529 --> 01:40:22,192
沒有任何合約 但是我相信拳王的團隊很清楚他們在做什么
No argument there. And I think the Zeus camp knows exactly what they're doing.

1234
01:40:22,299 --> 01:40:23,732
那就是他們做的 來吧
That they do. Come on.

1235
01:40:23,834 --> 01:40:26,860
給一個無名小卒一個機會來挑戰
Giving a shot at the belt to a nobody from nowhere.

1236
01:40:27,171 --> 01:40:30,265
那個垃圾廠的挑戰者？這一切都只是噱頭罷了
This "junkyard dog," if you will. That's a marketing stunt.

1237
01:40:30,374 --> 01:40:33,172
而且從觀眾的反應看起來 很奏效！
And judging from this crowd, that stunt is working.

1238
01:40:47,424 --> 01:40:48,789
我們贏不了 是吧？
We can't win, can we?

1239
01:40:49,827 --> 01:40:50,919
很難說
We'll see.

1240
01:40:55,299 --> 01:40:57,494
挑戰者正慢慢的走到他的角落
As the challenger makes his way into the arena,

1241
01:40:57,601 --> 01:40:59,796
你可以感受到激情的洶涌
you can hear the surge of excitement.

1242
01:41:11,315 --> 01:41:14,614
Atom已經抵達WRB的比賽現場
Atom has arrived onto the WRB scene with a vengeance,

1243
01:41:14,718 --> 01:41:17,516
用他“像人類”的外觀
using a style, some would call it human-like,

1244
01:41:17,621 --> 01:41:20,215
他戰斗的模式是非常少見的
that bot fighting has rarely seen.

1245
01:41:20,324 --> 01:41:22,519
Atom 跟他的迷你訓練員已經踏上比賽場地
Atom and his pint-size trainer step into the ring

1246
01:41:22,626 --> 01:41:25,493
看看法羅的表情 說明了一切
and the look on Farra Lemkova's face says it all.

1247
01:41:25,596 --> 01:41:27,757
歡迎來到大聯盟 年輕人
Welcome to the bigs, junior!

1248
01:41:27,865 --> 01:41:30,698
現在的賭盤開出來是1賠5 賭Atom撐不過第一回合
I'm giving one-to-five odds that Atom don't make it out the first round.

1249
01:41:30,801 --> 01:41:32,291
有人要賭嗎？
Who wants some?

1250
01:41:32,936 --> 01:41:34,631
現在可以開始下注了
I'll take some of that action.

1251
01:41:34,738 --> 01:41:37,901
嗨 我要下注
Hey, there! I'll take some of that action.

1252
01:41:39,243 --> 01:41:42,303
最近如何... 伙伴？
How's it going... partner?

1253
01:41:42,412 --> 01:41:43,777
誰是你的伙伴？
Partner?

1254
01:41:44,348 --> 01:41:47,511
很好 我下十萬 怎么樣？刺不刺激？
That's great. How about a hundred K? Is that funny?

1255
01:41:47,618 --> 01:41:50,280
十萬？賭Atom 撐不過第一回合？
Hundred K says Atom doesn't see round two.

1256
01:41:50,387 --> 01:41:52,218
你有帶那么多現金？
You carrying around that kind of scratch?

1257
01:41:53,490 --> 01:41:55,720
- 耶 - 十萬？
- Yeah. - Hundred K?

1258
01:41:56,426 --> 01:42:00,658
記得 我在101區 C 排
Tell you what. Remember section 101, row C,

1259
01:42:00,764 --> 01:42:03,460
然后把我的錢拿過來
and you can bring me my money right to my seat.

1260
01:42:03,567 --> 01:42:06,934
101 C排 ？十萬 ？
101, row C? Hundred K?

1261
01:42:07,704 --> 01:42:08,966
你聽到的 “宅男”！
You heard me, homey.

1262
01:42:09,273 --> 01:42:10,934
-宅男 ？- 是的 ？
- Homey? - Right?

1263
01:42:11,241 --> 01:42:12,401
宅在家里的大男孩
Homeboy!

1264
01:42:13,577 --> 01:42:15,909
沒事 保鏢們 酷！
All right. Peace out, posse.

1265
01:42:16,213 --> 01:42:17,510
來吧甜心 我們走吧
Come on, sugar. Let's go.

1266
01:42:41,305 --> 01:42:43,933
- 永遠不敗的 - 表演時間
- Never beaten. - It's showtime!

1267
01:42:44,241 --> 01:42:46,334
永不恐懼的
Never threatened.

1268
01:42:46,443 --> 01:42:49,606
拳擊場上的王者
The king of the ring,

1269
01:42:49,713 --> 01:42:51,840
機器人的統治者
the ruler of robots!

1270
01:42:53,016 --> 01:42:58,352
歡迎我們王者宙斯！
Bow down to the mighty Zeus!

1271
01:43:23,981 --> 01:43:25,005
哦！shit ！
Oh, shit!

1272
01:43:31,588 --> 01:43:32,885
好屌！
That was awesome.

1273
01:43:39,563 --> 01:43:40,723
來吧 我們走
Come on, let's go.

1274
01:43:47,504 --> 01:43:50,064
各位先生女士們
Ladies and gentlemen,

1275
01:43:50,374 --> 01:43:52,899
在五回合的拳擊規則下
in a bout scheduled for five rounds

1276
01:43:53,010 --> 01:43:56,446
進行世界拳擊冠軍大賽
for the World Robot Boxing Championship,

1277
01:43:56,546 --> 01:44:01,074
在我右手邊的是 挑戰者Atom
in the corner to my right, the challenger, Atom!

1278
01:44:01,318 --> 01:44:02,444
表現一下
Showboat!

1279
01:44:06,390 --> 01:44:08,790
以及 在我左邊的是...
And in the corner to my left,

1280
01:44:08,892 --> 01:44:11,918
整個宇宙最偉大的......
the undeniable champion of this universe

1281
01:44:12,029 --> 01:44:15,624
以及所有宇宙最厲害的...
and any other universe known or unknown,

1282
01:44:15,732 --> 01:44:19,964
宙斯王者
the mighty Zeus!

1283
01:44:24,541 --> 01:44:28,739
現在 各位先生女士們準備好
And now, ladies and gentlemen, are you ready

1284
01:44:28,845 --> 01:44:33,839
鋼鐵擂臺
for Real Steel!

1285
01:44:36,787 --> 01:44:37,947
就是我們期待已久的！
This is what it's all about!

1286
01:44:38,055 --> 01:44:42,048
鈴聲響起 馬上開始比賽了
There's the starting bell and we are underway.

1287
01:44:42,359 --> 01:44:44,088
機器人慢慢的離開他們的角落
The bots emerge from their corners.

1288
01:44:44,995 --> 01:44:48,055
宙斯一下就把Atom打趴 Atom已經倒下了
Zeus decks Atom, and he is already down.

1289
01:44:48,365 --> 01:44:49,491
站起來！
On your feet!

1290
01:44:49,599 --> 01:44:52,067
看來又是一出宙斯式的慘劇
Looks like we are in for another Zeus clinic.

1291
01:44:54,538 --> 01:44:56,938
裁判馬特蓋格已經出來開始倒數了
Referee Matt Geiger coming in the ring to start the count.

1292
01:44:58,008 --> 01:44:59,066
站起來！
Get up!

1293
01:45:00,744 --> 01:45:02,905
用手撐起來！站起來！
Push up! Stand up!

1294
01:45:03,947 --> 01:45:06,541
但是看看 小巨人已經站起來了
But look at this. The little bot's back on his feet

1295
01:45:06,650 --> 01:45:09,118
準備迎接宙斯的第二輪猛攻
to get a second blistering attack from Zeus!

1296
01:45:09,419 --> 01:45:12,411
不到十秒時間 Atom又一次倒下了
Atom is down for the second time in less than ten seconds.

1297
01:45:12,522 --> 01:45:16,481
- 太強了 - 好樣的 那才像我的人！
- He's too strong! - That's my boy right there!

1298
01:45:18,495 --> 01:45:20,019
站起來繼續比賽
Get up and get in the game!

1299
01:45:20,130 --> 01:45:23,156
來吧！ 不 拜托 Atom 站起來！
Come on! No, please Atom, get up! Please!

1300
01:45:23,467 --> 01:45:25,992
站起來！ 站起來！ 站起來！
Get up! Get up! Get up!

1301
01:45:27,637 --> 01:45:31,038
又一次 挑戰者站了起來！
Once again, the challenger finds his feet!

1302
01:45:31,641 --> 01:45:32,665
低頭 后退！
Lean back!

1303
01:45:32,776 --> 01:45:35,074
Atom被連續擊逼到了繩索邊上
Atom's getting pummeled into the corner!

1304
01:45:35,178 --> 01:45:37,544
- 離開角落！ - 移動！
- Get out of there! - Move!

1305
01:45:39,816 --> 01:45:41,875
一陣摧毀式的近身攻擊
A demolishing inside shot.

1306
01:45:41,985 --> 01:45:43,111
把手舉起來！
Get your hands up!

1307
01:45:45,122 --> 01:45:46,680
舉起來！
Hands up!

1308
01:45:47,624 --> 01:45:49,057
揍扁那個罐頭
Crush that little can!

1309
01:45:49,159 --> 01:45:50,649
離開角落
Get out of the corner!

1310
01:45:50,761 --> 01:45:54,060
肯頓絕望的命令他的機器人離開死亡的角落
Kenton desperately trying to command his robot out of that suicide corner.

1311
01:45:59,002 --> 01:46:00,060
蹲低一點！
Get your feet under you!

1312
01:46:01,738 --> 01:46:03,797
晚安 表演機器人！
Good night, sparring bot!

1313
01:46:03,907 --> 01:46:06,637
今晚只是時間長了一點 但是宙斯又一次要擊倒了...
It might have taken Zeus a bit longer, but he's done it again!

1314
01:46:06,743 --> 01:46:10,076
Atom第三次倒下了 也可能是今晚最后一次倒下
Atom is down for the third and possibly final time tonight.

1315
01:46:10,180 --> 01:46:12,546
- 站起來！ - 2！
- Stand up! - Two!

1316
01:46:12,649 --> 01:46:14,048
3！
Three!

1317
01:46:14,151 --> 01:46:15,516
Atom 站起來！
Atom, get up!

1318
01:46:15,619 --> 01:46:17,678
- 起來 Atom - 起來 Atom
- Get up, Atom. - Get up, Atom.

1319
01:46:18,188 --> 01:46:21,055
- 6 ！7！ - 起來！
- Six! Seven! - Get up!

1320
01:46:21,158 --> 01:46:23,058
8！ 9！
Eight! Nine!

1321
01:46:24,094 --> 01:46:28,622
真不敢相信！似曾相識 小巨人又一次站了起來
I don't believe this! Against all odds, this little bot is on his feet again.

1322
01:46:29,800 --> 01:46:30,892
來吧 Atom！
Come on, Atom!

1323
01:46:34,037 --> 01:46:35,197
它撐不下去的
He can't survive this!

1324
01:46:39,009 --> 01:46:41,204
- 來吧 Charlie！ - 右上勾拳
- Come on, Charlie! - Right uppercut!

1325
01:46:42,646 --> 01:46:45,240
Atom 使出一記絕招！
Atom has landed a punch!

1326
01:46:45,549 --> 01:46:50,577
宙斯被出乎意料的上鉤拳擊中 搖晃的退后
Zeus is stunned as he reels back from an uppercut that he never saw coming!

1327
01:46:50,687 --> 01:46:52,120
前進！
Advance!

1328
01:46:52,222 --> 01:46:53,712
退一步 出右拳！
Fade back, counter right!

1329
01:46:54,524 --> 01:46:55,684
退一步 出右拳！
Fade back, counter right!

1330
01:46:56,526 --> 01:47:00,963
右交叉拳！ 右交叉拳！ 右交叉拳！ 左勾拳！
Right cross! Right cross! Right cross! Left hook!

1331
01:47:01,064 --> 01:47:03,931
- 來吧！ 上吧！ - 擊倒他！
- Let's go! Come on! - Take him down!

1332
01:47:04,601 --> 01:47:06,660
第一次 Atom占了優勢
For the first time in his dominant run,

1333
01:47:06,770 --> 01:47:10,638
宙斯第一次遇到一個打不退的對手
Zeus has met a bot who simply won't back down!

1334
01:47:12,275 --> 01:47:15,108
群眾已經瘋狂了 宙斯使出渾身解數
The crowd is going nuts! Zeus gives it everything he's got

1335
01:47:15,212 --> 01:47:18,181
第一回合已經剩下15秒鐘了
as we reach the last 15 seconds of round one!

1336
01:47:18,281 --> 01:47:22,240
宙斯把Atom逼到角落 使出雙組合拳
Zeus corners Atom, going double duty with both fists!

1337
01:47:22,552 --> 01:47:25,544
上擊 下擊！好像鐘擺上上下下
Downtown, uptown, as the clock winds down!

1338
01:47:25,655 --> 01:47:28,715
- 手舉起來 下巴壓低 - 蹲低一點 蹲低一點
- Hands up, chin down. - Stay low, stay low!

1339
01:47:32,229 --> 01:47:37,292
只剩5秒鐘 拳王使出了活塞式的組合拳
Only five seconds left, as here comes that piston-packed right of the champ!

1340
01:47:38,835 --> 01:47:42,999
鈴聲響起了 不敢相信 Atom竟然撐過了第一回合
There's the bell! I don't believe it. Somehow Atom has survived.

1341
01:47:43,106 --> 01:47:48,169
竟然進到了第二回合 觀眾都起雞皮疙瘩了
We will have a second round. And the crowd here is thrilled!

1342
01:47:51,281 --> 01:47:54,614
他辦到了！ 耶！ 回來角落！
He made it! Yeah! Corner!

1343
01:47:56,086 --> 01:47:59,920
我們要趕快離開這里 馬上！
We got to get out of here. We got to get out of here now!

1344
01:48:02,726 --> 01:48:05,024
走另外一邊 快點！
We got to go this way. Come on!

1345
01:48:10,600 --> 01:48:11,897
好吧 你坐下吧！
OK, you sit down.

1346
01:48:15,071 --> 01:48:17,767
- 走吧 宅男 - 好啦
- Let's go, homey. - All right.

1347
01:48:17,874 --> 01:48:19,307
我一會就回來 寶貝
I'll be back for you, baby.

1348
01:48:20,277 --> 01:48:22,609
把你的手拿開 我自己走
Get your hands off me!

1349
01:48:25,015 --> 01:48:27,950
二個角落都在忙的檢查他們的機器人
Both corners furiously working on their bots.

1350
01:48:28,051 --> 01:48:31,384
觀眾們本來都預期今晚是個大屠殺
This crowd came here tonight expecting a massacre,

1351
01:48:31,688 --> 01:48:33,679
但是迎來的是一場勢均力敵的戰斗
but instead they're getting a war!

1352
01:48:33,790 --> 01:48:35,121
- 你弄好了嗎？- 耶
- You got it? - Yeah.

1353
01:48:35,225 --> 01:48:36,249
好樣的 來吧！繼續！
All right. Here we go.

1354
01:48:36,359 --> 01:48:38,657
怎么搞的？
What is happening?

1355
01:48:38,762 --> 01:48:43,756
他已經完全準備好應付任何突發狀況 沒有事的
He is fully prepared for all possible contingencies. He will be fine.

1356
01:48:43,867 --> 01:48:45,164
然后呢？
What next?

1357
01:48:46,036 --> 01:48:47,333
第二回合
Round two.

1358
01:48:55,645 --> 01:48:58,944
Atom 第二回合 Atom 不可思議的挑戰者
Round two kicks off, and incredibly the challenger, Atom,

1359
01:48:59,049 --> 01:49:01,074
勇敢的挑戰拳王
is giving the champ a run for his money.

1360
01:49:02,819 --> 01:49:06,414
宙斯揣著小巨人 把它像個罐子丟到繩邊
Zeus tosses the smaller bot across the ring like a tin can!

1361
01:49:10,193 --> 01:49:15,187
肯頓讓他的機器人打出一個三連擊 打在拳王的臉上！
Kenton working his bot with a trifecta of straight rights to the champ's dome!

1362
01:49:20,236 --> 01:49:24,229
他們并列在戰場 震耳欲聾的歡呼聲
Toe-to-toe they stand, trading deafening blows!

1363
01:49:27,310 --> 01:49:31,076
不管繩圈旁的教練想什么伎倆都沒有用了
Whatever strategy either corner had cooked up has been destroyed!

1364
01:49:33,917 --> 01:49:37,250
金屬對戰金屬 鋼鐵大戰鋼鐵
Metal bashing metal. Steel smashing steel.

1365
01:49:37,354 --> 01:49:39,754
這是一場大戰
This is a brawl!

1366
01:49:42,359 --> 01:49:47,262
觀眾已經都站起來了 拉長脖子看二個機器人殘殺對方
The crowd is on their feet, watching two machines driven to kill each other!

1367
01:49:47,364 --> 01:49:50,060
也即將要發生什么大事了
Something has to give, and it does!

1368
01:49:50,166 --> 01:49:51,997
Atom 又一次倒下了
Atom goes down again!

1369
01:49:52,102 --> 01:49:56,232
今晚再一次次的點亮惡斗的戰場
Lights out for the junkyard dog who put on a heck of a show here tonight!

1370
01:49:58,341 --> 01:50:01,003
又一次 Atom又站起來了
And yet again, Atom rises up.

1371
01:50:01,111 --> 01:50:05,707
肯頓逼不得已要跳線接上 才可以使機器人回到比賽
Kenton must have hardwired this bot with the will to go on!

1372
01:50:12,022 --> 01:50:17,050
第四回合中段 拳王想馬上擊倒對手 結束比賽
Midway through round four, and Zeus is looking to end this thing right now.

1373
01:50:17,160 --> 01:50:21,494
拳王已經豁出一切 好像不打算回到更衣室了
The champ is holding nothing back as he cracks open the hurt locker!

1374
01:50:31,775 --> 01:50:35,472
Atom在繩索邊搖搖晃晃 他已經昏了！
Atom is stumbling around the ring, apparently disoriented and dazed!

1375
01:50:35,779 --> 01:50:37,178
- 手舉起來！ - 出了什么事？
- Hands up! - What's going on?

1376
01:50:37,280 --> 01:50:40,215
我猜語音控制已經壞掉了 沒有反應！
I think the voice recog is shot! He's not responding!

1377
01:50:43,453 --> 01:50:48,220
宙斯就像完美的暴力武器 鉆進Atom的腹部
Zeus has found yet another gear of violence, drilling Atom's midsection.

1378
01:50:48,324 --> 01:50:51,521
不！住手！幫一下手啊！
No! Stop! Do something!

1379
01:50:51,828 --> 01:50:52,852
他已經聽不到了！
He can't hear me!

1380
01:50:54,197 --> 01:50:59,829
但是鈴聲又響起了 小機器人的表現已經震驚了整個世界
But the bell sounds, and once again this little robot has stunned the world!

1381
01:51:01,938 --> 01:51:06,341
我們完蛋了 Max 他聽不到我的語音指揮了 這是謀殺 我們認輸吧！
We're done, Max! He can't hear me. This is murder. We've had enough.

1382
01:51:06,443 --> 01:51:09,003
- 我把語音辨識關掉了 - 又怎樣？他聽不到我的聲音了
- I'm disabling the voice recognition. - He can't hear me!

1383
01:51:09,112 --> 01:51:11,444
- 是的 但是他看得到你！ - 你說什么？
- Yes, but he can see you! - What?

1384
01:51:12,916 --> 01:51:15,817
我切換到映射模式 你要教他怎么做
I'm putting him in shadow mode. Show him what to do.

1385
01:51:15,919 --> 01:51:18,285
不用語音辨識模式 它可以移動的更快
Without the voice recognition, he'll move even faster!

1386
01:51:18,388 --> 01:51:19,548
不行 不行！
No way. No way!

1387
01:51:19,856 --> 01:51:21,824
看看他們 他們已經被打暈了！
Look at them. They are freaking out!

1388
01:51:22,325 --> 01:51:24,384
那個有錢女孩已經抓著他指指點點了！
Rich girl is ripping him a new one over there!

1389
01:51:24,494 --> 01:51:26,519
你知道為什么嗎？因為他們已經害怕了
Do you know why? Because they're scared.

1390
01:51:26,830 --> 01:51:28,991
因為Atom可以做到其他機器人做不到的
Because Atom can do things no other bot has ever done.

1391
01:51:29,099 --> 01:51:30,964
- 但是我做不到 - 行的 你可以的
- But I can't do it! - Yes, you can.

1392
01:51:31,067 --> 01:51:33,865
- 我不行啦 - 不 你行的
- I can't. - Yes, you can.

1393
01:51:35,004 --> 01:51:38,462
讓他知道怎么做 你必須自己戰斗最后一個回合
Show him what to do. You have to fight the last round.

1394
01:51:38,775 --> 01:51:40,140
不要拜托我 不要
Don't ask me. Don't.

1395
01:51:40,243 --> 01:51:44,839
Charlie... 拜托 我求你
Charlie... please. I beg you.

1396
01:51:53,490 --> 01:51:54,980
你要用那個小狗眼神“殺”死我？
Are you kidding me with those eyes?

1397
01:51:56,860 --> 01:51:58,327
該死的！
Damn it!

1398
01:51:58,428 --> 01:51:59,486
耶！
Yes!

1399
01:52:00,296 --> 01:52:01,888
真不敢相信我會這么做
I can't believe I'm doing this.

1400
01:52:02,966 --> 01:52:05,332
我知道你能了解 不管你是不是聽得到
I know you're in there! I'm not sure if you're getting this or what,

1401
01:52:05,435 --> 01:52:06,868
但是我確定你了解
but I know you're in there!

1402
01:52:06,970 --> 01:52:09,234
- 肯頓 打還是不打？- 打 給我一分鐘
- Kenton. In or out? - In. Give me a minute.

1403
01:52:12,842 --> 01:52:17,404
我知道你聽不見我說的 但是你可以看得到我 所以看著我
I know you can't hear me, but you can see me, so watch me!

1404
01:52:17,514 --> 01:52:20,176
仔細看著...我
Watch... me.

1405
01:52:20,283 --> 01:52:23,946
- 你知道你是對一個機器人講話 - 我知道 閉嘴！
- You know you're talking to a robot. - I know. Shut up.

1406
01:52:25,054 --> 01:52:26,612
注意看著我
Watch me.

1407
01:52:27,090 --> 01:52:29,081
這場如史詩般的大戰已經
An epic battle being waged here tonight,

1408
01:52:29,192 --> 01:52:31,285
馬上要進入第五回合 最后的一個回合
as the fifth and final round gets underway.

1409
01:52:31,394 --> 01:52:33,021
來吧 Atom！
Come on, Atom!

1410
01:52:42,539 --> 01:52:44,939
等一下 你有沒有看到？
Wait a second. Are you seeing this?

1411
01:52:45,041 --> 01:52:48,169
Charlie肯頓正在場外映射指導回擊
Charlie Kenton is shadowboxing just outside the ring!

1412
01:52:48,278 --> 01:52:50,473
看來Atom有動作映射功能
It looks like Atom has a shadow function.

1413
01:52:50,580 --> 01:52:53,447
所以基本上 Charlie肯頓就像是
So, basically, that means Charlie Kenton

1414
01:52:53,550 --> 01:52:56,417
在最后一個回合自己上場對抗宙斯
is fighting the last round of this fight against Zeus.

1415
01:52:56,519 --> 01:53:01,115
但是看起來一點幫助都沒有 Atom又被逼到了角落
It doesn't seem to help, because Atom is backed up against the ropes again.

1416
01:53:03,159 --> 01:53:05,059
幫幫他！ 還擊！
Help him! Fight back!

1417
01:53:05,161 --> 01:53:06,253
還不到時候
Not yet.

1418
01:53:09,866 --> 01:53:13,597
松本親自監督宙斯的操作人員
Tak Mashido supervising personally as Zeus hammers down,

1419
01:53:13,903 --> 01:53:16,633
憤怒的想馬上擊倒Atom 結束比賽
furiously trying to end this thing once and for all.

1420
01:53:17,640 --> 01:53:20,666
告訴各位大家 拳王看起來累了
I got to tell you, folks, the champ looks tired.

1421
01:53:20,977 --> 01:53:23,207
拳王看起來已經沒力了
This robot seems to be running on empty.

1422
01:53:27,050 --> 01:53:29,382
不敢相信！Atom在挑釁宙斯
I don't believe it. Atom is taunting Zeus.

1423
01:53:29,485 --> 01:53:33,114
- 切換到渦輪加速！ - 他認為還不夠！
- Switch to turbo! - He's actually asking for more.

1424
01:53:35,091 --> 01:53:36,615
拜托救救他！
Please do something!

1425
01:53:36,926 --> 01:53:39,156
- 還不到時候 - 對了 Charlie 還沒到時候
- Not yet. - That's right, Charlie. Not yet.

1426
01:53:41,931 --> 01:53:43,296
現在使出活塞拳！
Nitrous pistons, now!

1427
01:53:46,436 --> 01:53:48,404
他已經沒有辦法再支持住了
He's not going to last much longer!

1428
01:53:48,504 --> 01:53:50,438
- 回擊！ - 還不到時候
- Fight back! - Not yet.

1429
01:53:51,207 --> 01:53:52,469
堅持住！
Hang in there!

1430
01:53:52,575 --> 01:53:58,036
Atom對宙斯的機關槍拳一點都沒有辦法招架
Atom is riddled with the nitrous-fueled Gatling guns of Zeus's blows!

1431
01:53:59,215 --> 01:54:03,049
Atom！ Atom！ Atom！ Atom！
Atom! Atom! Atom! Atom!

1432
01:54:06,356 --> 01:54:08,483
等他沒力 等他力竭！ 還沒！
Wait him out, wait him out! Not yet!

1433
01:54:11,094 --> 01:54:13,187
宙斯慢下來了！
Zeus is slowing down!

1434
01:54:13,296 --> 01:54:16,163
拳王的動力已經接近報廢了
The champ's power core is clearly depleted.

1435
01:54:16,266 --> 01:54:17,324
Charlie 拜托！
Charlie, please!

1436
01:54:19,569 --> 01:54:20,661
嗨 小鬼！
Hey, kid.

1437
01:54:21,537 --> 01:54:23,129
- 時候到了 - 現在！
- Now. - Now!

1438
01:54:28,411 --> 01:54:29,469
靠近他！
Get in there!

1439
01:54:32,048 --> 01:54:34,312
揍扁這個婊子 打的他開花！
Knock that little bitch! Bust him open!

1440
01:54:43,259 --> 01:54:44,624
耶！ 這就對了！
Yeah! That's right!

1441
01:54:46,195 --> 01:54:47,423
想想辦法！！
Do something!

1442
01:54:48,298 --> 01:54:49,356
走開！
Move!

1443
01:54:50,733 --> 01:54:53,224
最高級別 切換到手動控制！
Override. Switching to manual.

1444
01:54:55,271 --> 01:55:00,106
松本吃驚的舉動 他竟然親手手動操作他的機器人
In a shocking move, Tak Mashido is manually operating his robot personally!

1445
01:55:10,553 --> 01:55:13,249
- 攻擊身體！ 靠近他！ - 打倒他 Atom！
- Work the body! Get inside him! - Get him, Atom!

1446
01:55:15,024 --> 01:55:19,518
大家看啊！拳王現在只能拼命的想辦法站著
Look at this! The champ is trying desperately to stay on his feet,

1447
01:55:19,629 --> 01:55:24,794
但是肯頓一點都不留情 一拳一拳的轟炸宙斯的身體！
but Kenton is relentless, landing blow after blow after blow to the body!

1448
01:56:07,210 --> 01:56:09,371
左！右！左！右！
Left! Right! Left! Right!

1449
01:56:09,479 --> 01:56:14,644
Atom打出一記重要的上勾拳！ 宙斯倒下了！
A huge uppercut by Atom! Zeus is down!

1450
01:56:19,355 --> 01:56:22,518
這個小機器人今天晚上的頑強表現
This little bot has dug deep here tonight

1451
01:56:22,625 --> 01:56:25,355
深深的觸動每一個人的心
and shown something damn near heart!

1452
01:56:25,461 --> 01:56:29,659
1 2 3......
One, two, three,

1453
01:56:29,766 --> 01:56:34,703
4 5 6 7......
four, five, six, seven...

1454
01:56:34,804 --> 01:56:35,828
宙斯站起來了！
He's good!

1455
01:56:36,139 --> 01:56:39,472
宙斯已經快站不住了 但是肯頓及...
Zeus gets to his feet, but Kenton has Atom on him again,

1456
01:56:39,575 --> 01:56:41,338
...Atom沒有放過他 拳如雨下！
landing punch after punch!

1457
01:56:41,444 --> 01:56:43,810
松本跟他的超級機器人一點都沒有辦法回應
Tak Mashido and his super bot have no answer.

1458
01:56:44,113 --> 01:56:47,207
宙斯夾住了Atom的左臂 但是肯頓一點都不懼怕
Zeus pins Atom's left arm, but Kenton is undaunted!

1459
01:56:47,316 --> 01:56:50,285
局面竟然到了這個地步 各位！
It all comes down to this, folks!

1460
01:56:50,386 --> 01:56:52,286
甩開他 Charlie！ 就是現在！
Drop him, Charlie! Now!

1461
01:56:52,388 --> 01:56:55,380
- 肯頓已經快把冠軍... - 不 鈴聲響起來了
- Kenton is about to drop the champ... - No! There's the bell!

1462
01:56:56,426 --> 01:56:58,621
鈴聲救了宙斯！！
Zeus is saved by the bell!

1463
01:57:05,535 --> 01:57:08,436
不可思議 比賽進入到裁判判決
Amazingly, we will go to the judges' cards!

1464
01:57:19,526 --> 01:57:20,686
去吧！

1465
01:57:22,118 --> 01:57:25,884
各位先生女士們 經過了五個艱苦的回合以后
Ladies and gentlemen, after five rounds,

1466
01:57:26,189 --> 01:57:28,749
裁判的判決已經出來了
we go to the judges' scorecards.

1467
01:57:32,695 --> 01:57:37,257
第一位裁判的判決 47-48
Judge Number One scores the fight 47-48.

1468
01:57:37,366 --> 01:57:42,326
第二位裁判的判決 48-46
Judge Number Two scores the fight 48-46.

1469
01:57:42,438 --> 01:57:47,171
第三為裁判的判決 47-46
And Judge Number Three scores the fight 47-46,

1470
01:57:47,276 --> 01:57:52,475
世界冠軍成功的保住了他的冠軍頭銜
for the winner and still World Robot Boxing champion,

1471
01:57:52,582 --> 01:57:54,880
宙斯！
Zeus!

1472
01:58:02,325 --> 01:58:04,486
法拉 蘭蔻娃
Farra Lemkova,

1473
01:58:04,594 --> 01:58:06,892
妳的機器人今天晚上的表現比你們說的差多了
you got way more than you bargained for tonight.

1474
01:58:07,196 --> 01:58:10,563
有人說你的機器人贏了判決 但是輸了比賽
Some would say that your bot won the decision but lost the fight.

1475
01:58:11,334 --> 01:58:12,596
她看起來很不爽
She looks pissed.

1476
01:58:13,302 --> 01:58:15,532
比賽過程比我們想象的還要久一點
It took a little longer than we thought,

1477
01:58:15,638 --> 01:58:18,835
但是結果還是如預期的一樣
but the result is as expected.

1478
01:58:20,276 --> 01:58:24,645
我們贏了 宙斯還是永遠不敗的
We won. Zeus is still undefeated.

1479
01:58:26,895 --> 01:58:28,895
松本先生 我想問的是...

1480
01:58:29,919 --> 01:58:33,252
對于你們今晚這場那么羞辱的比賽 被慘痛的修理...
Any comment on the absolutely humiliating near loss

1481
01:58:33,356 --> 01:58:34,618
...還差點輸了 你有沒有話要說？
your bot suffered tonight?

1482
01:58:37,627 --> 01:58:40,255
- 沒說 - 不予置評
- Nothing. - No comment.

1483
01:58:40,363 --> 01:58:41,694
Max Max在哪里？
Max. Where's Max?

1484
01:58:45,368 --> 01:58:46,528
他在那里...Max！
There he is. Max.

1485
01:58:48,304 --> 01:58:51,705
大家都稱你的機器人是“平民冠軍"
They're already calling your bot "the people's champion."

1486
01:58:55,244 --> 01:58:57,007
你怎么說呢？
What do you say to that?

1487
01:58:57,980 --> 01:58:59,470
平民冠軍？
People's champion?

1488
01:59:01,918 --> 01:59:03,442
對我來說 很好！
Sounds pretty good to me.

1489
01:59:09,358 --> 01:59:11,417
爹？爹！
Dad? Dad!

1490
01:59:15,398 --> 01:59:16,558
爹！
Dad!

1491
01:59:27,476 --> 01:59:29,000
我真的想讓你知道
I really want you to know...

1492
01:59:29,312 --> 01:59:31,371
不 你需要知道...
No, I need you to know.

1493
01:59:33,482 --> 01:59:34,710
不用擔心
Don't worry.

1494
01:59:35,718 --> 01:59:37,481
我會保密的
Your secret's safe with me.

1495
01:59:44,527 --> 01:59:46,290
等一下！
Wait here. Wait here.

1496
02:00:30,973 --> 02:00:32,668
耶！
Yes!

1497
02:00:35,918 --> 02:00:36,918
翻譯：閑閑的猛男 校對：目前沒有

